      <title>达美航空因灾难性系统故障损失 5 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/delta-air-says-system-outage-will-cost-the-carrier-500-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[达美航空公司 (Delta Air Lines Inc.) 本月因技术故障而面临 5 亿美元的负面影响，此次故障导致数千个航班被取消，并损害了该航空公司的声誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/delta-air-says-system-outage-will-cost-the-carrier-500-million</guid>
